name: TorontoGuide
0:
”Alexa, Open Toronto Guide”
”Tell me some tips to get around”
”Alexa, Open Toronto Guide and give me an attraction.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: toronto guide
des:
Thinking about what to do in Toronto? This app can definitely help you with your travel plans. Simply say "Open Toronto Guide" to get started.
- Ask for top 5 things to do
- Ask for tips on getting around
- Ask for an attraction to go to

This app contains information for over 15 attractions, with more on the way!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
